<%= form_for @boat do |f| %>

Name of Vessel: <%= f.text_field :name %>

Home Port: <%= f.text_field :location %> <!-- use google maps to confirm -->

Choose type of vessel: <%= f.text_field :boat_type %> <!-- make a drop down from list -->

Choose capacity: <%= f.number_field :capacity %> <!-- make a drop down from list, max 15+ -->

Price per day: <%= f.number_field :price %>

Add description of your cool ass vessel: <%= f.text_area :description %>

Upload a photo of your boat: <%= f.file_field :photo %>

TEMP use user_id 1 or 2: <%= f.number_field :user_id %>

<%= f.submit %>
<% end %>




